            				<header class='rail-article-titles'>
            					<h1 class='h5'>Bolaño in Girona: A Friendship</h1>
            					<address class='p'>By Javier Cercas</address>
            					<time class='p'>October 15, 2024</time>
            				</header>
            			</a>
            		</article>
                                		<article class='rail-article'>
            			<a href='https://www.theparisreview.org/blog/?post_type=post&p=168793'>
            				<div class='rail-figure-wrap'>
            					<figure>
